{
  "stem": "27409.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "He left on the table bread, a piece of cheese, which I swallowed, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He closed his eyes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He couldn't give me, so-- and I collected rest of cigarettes, which were on the table.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I collected, brought them with me, which was for barter very good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I-- most important, he was reading papers, the German army papers, and the Romanian papers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So I could read from all sorts of papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I don't know if he saw it or not, because we were not permitted to read papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I was expected when I came in the-- I became the newspaper of the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I brought always-- sometime I adjusted it in our form to give them hope.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "In particular, [INAUDIBLE] retreat in some places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "So was a big retreat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But it helped the people to keep up the morale.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And he wanted me near, so he put me as sort of an [INAUDIBLE] clerk in the office.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I had to check how many people at work are there in different parts of the mine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And to measure the ready production, which was sent to a former synagogue, which had been transformed, or was being-- was transformed, also by Jewish forced labors, into a factory to make bricks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Jews also worked on the railway from the synagogue to the railway station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It was not a pleasant work, always beating, beating, beating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "We survived, and in-- it was in September.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was at the time of Yom Kippur, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I had heard that he-- what he did with the Jewish women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "He used to try to the breasts, and the Jewish woman push back her chest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "So hit in the genitalia, or hit in genitalia and then to grab the breast.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
